title: Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar Writings and Speeches [audio+pdf] Part 1
description:
This torrent contains audio recordings of 4 volumes (vol 1, 2, 3 & 4) + pdfs of all the 17 volumes of "Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar Writings and Speeches" as published by Ministry of Social Justice & Empowerment, Govt. of India.

The recordings themselves have been created by Ministry of External Affairs, Govt. of India. And have been posted on MEA, Govt. Of India's SoundCloud account. Few audio recordings are incomplete/missing though as MEA didn't recorded all of them completely.

Please set seeding for this torrent as "unlimited" in your torrent client so that maximum no. of people can get the benefits of these precious audio recordings and pdf documents
